This directory, v8, contains tests which
are related to the development of the various development in
version 8.x.x of Abinit

Please, see the README file in the tests directory (above this one) to get help.


------------------------------------------------------------------

* Tests 1-40 concern ground state 

* Tests 41-79 concern response functions

* Tests 80-99 concern GW/BSE

* Tests 100-109 concern Nonlinear(+PAW) and 2nd order Sternheimer equation

------------------------------------------------------------------
